<h3>4. LOGO生成</h3>
<p>1）logo生成流程</p>
<p><img data-action="zoom" class="aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/09/EKiPb2D9o8fg9KYgPsmE.png" alt="" width="740" height="321" /></p>
<p>2）logo生成原型</p>
<p><img data-action="zoom" class="aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/09/TDG8GGEyPLoMIVfXpDlW.png" alt="" width="1991" height="3107" /></p>
<p>3）logo展示原型</p>
<p><img data-action="zoom" class="aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/09/QAMlRfMXsLRUCNAVfhlZ.png" alt="" width="1279" height="1507" /></p>
<p>4）logo编辑流程</p>
